This is the README file for CPANPLUS::Dist::PAR, a CPANPLUS extension 
for perl package to debian package conversion.

Please refer to 'perldoc CPANPLUS::Dist::PAR' after installation for 
details.

#####################################################################

* Description

CPANPLUS::Dist::PAR

    CPANPLUS::Dist::PAR is a CPANPLUS plugin that allows you to 
    create PAR archives from CPAN packages. This is as easy as
    passing an extra option to the installation process or setting
    a config option.
    

#####################################################################

* Installation

CPANPLUS::Dist::PAR follows the standard perl module install process

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

The module uses no C or XS parts, so no c-compiler is required.

